data.description: Welcome to Rosena Ranch! This delightful home with Loft and Downstairs 4th Bedroom with full private bath presents an inviting open floor plan that is both spacious and warmly intimate.    Upon entering, you will be impressed by the natural light that fills the open space throughout the family room and kitchen. The kitchen would delight any culinary enthusiast. The granite countertops and extended island offer ample space for preparation and entertainment, while the walk-in pantry with its custom Dutch door adds a touch of rustic charm. The family room, cozy with its crackling fireplace, is the perfect backdrop for memorable moments.    The downstairs bedroom/ in-law suite is a serene retreat which affords picturesque Mountain View and is serviced by a full, private bathroom, providing guests with comfort and privacy. Upstairs, you will find the oversized loft, adaptable to your heart's desire—be it a game room, study, or additional family space.    The primary bedroom, expansive and inviting, promises a sanctuary of relaxation. A custom barn door reveals an ensuite bathroom, complete with dual sinks and an oversized soaking tub, perfect for indulgent evenings. The walk-in closet is as spacious as it is practical, ensuring a place for every cherished item.    Fresh paint and new flooring throughout the home echo the care and attention to detail evident in every corner.    Residents of Rosena Ranch are welcomed by community amenities that cater to every age and interest. From the Olympic-sized pool to unwind on sunny days, a spa for tranquil evenings, the splash pad for joyous family fun, and basketball courts for the sportively inclined. The gym, clubhouse, and meeting rooms enhance the sense of community, ensuring every day is an opportunity for new experiences.
